    <item>
      <title>加纳获得债务减免条款，足以为国际货币基金组织释放 6 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ghana-gets-debt-relief-terms-enough-to-unlock-imf-600-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳财政部长肯·奥福里-阿塔 (Ken Ofori-Atta) 表示，加纳已收到官方债权人提供的债务减免条款清单草案，该草案足以让国际货币基金组织向这个西非国家支付 6 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/ghana-gets-debt-relief-terms-enough-to-unlock-imf-600-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>热门消费者物价指数数据公布后，随着债券波动，股市下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街股市波动较大，通胀数据超出预期，削弱了对美联储 3 月份降息的押注，股市下跌，债券也难以寻找方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 22:43:58 GMT</pubDate>
